### Send a normal order
POST http://localhost:5000/order
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item_id": "ITEM-001",
  "quantity": 1,
  "amount": 50.0
}

### ─── FAULT INJECTION ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Inject payment crash (circuit breaker test)
POST http://localhost:5001/fault/crash
Content-Type: application/json

{ "enabled": true }

### Set payment fail rate 70%
POST http://localhost:5001/fault/fail_rate
Content-Type: application/json

{ "rate": 0.7 }

### Check circuit breaker state
GET http://localhost:5001/payment/health

### Reset circuit breaker
POST http://localhost:5001/fault/cb/reset

### Inject inventory latency (timeout test)
POST http://localhost:5002/fault/latency
Content-Type: application/json

{ "enabled": true, "latency_ms": 5000 }

### Exhaust inventory thread pool (bulkhead test)
POST http://localhost:5002/fault/exhaust
Content-Type: application/json

{ "enabled": true }

### Set notification transient failure rate (retry test)
POST http://localhost:5003/fault/transient
Content-Type: application/json

{ "rate": 0.8 }

### ─── RESET ALL FAULTS ────────────────────────────────────────

### Reset order faults
POST http://localhost:5000/fault/reset

### Reset payment faults
POST http://localhost:5001/fault/reset

### Reset inventory faults
POST http://localhost:5002/fault/reset

### Reset notification faults
POST http://localhost:5003/fault/reset

### Reset inventory stock
POST http://localhost:5002/inventory/stock/reset

### ─── HEALTH CHECKS ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Order health
GET http://localhost:5000/order/health

### Payment health + CB state
GET http://localhost:5001/payment/health

### Inventory health + pool status
GET http://localhost:5002/inventory/health

### Notification health + retry config
GET http://localhost:5003/notify/health

### View current stock
GET http://localhost:5002/inventory/stock